00:20:09,060 --> 00:20:11,127
(Ginuwine's "Pony" begins)

498
00:20:11,162 --> 00:20:13,196
- Uh, you are?
- I'm Artie Abrams,

499
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:15,298
and I'll be singing
"Pony" by Ginuwine.

500
00:20:16,334 --> 00:20:20,036
♪ I'm just a bachelor ♪

501
